%%{init: {'theme': 'dark', 'themeVariables': { 'fontSize': '14px' }}}%%

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as 👤 Usuario
    participant C as 🛡️ Caddy<br/>:443
    participant A as 🔐 Authelia<br/>SSO/MFA
    participant N as ☁️ Nextcloud<br/>:8080
    participant R as ⚡ Redis<br/>Session
    participant D as 🗄️ MySQL<br/>Database

    Note over U,D: 🔒 SECURE AUTHENTICATION FLOW

    U->>C: HTTPS Request<br/>nextcloud.alvarezconsult.es
    activate C
    
    Note right of C: TLS 1.3 Encryption
    
    C->>A: forward_auth verify<br/>GET /api/verify
    activate A
    
    alt No Valid Session
        A-->>C: 302 Redirect<br/>→ Login Portal
        C-->>U: Redirect to<br/>authelia.alvarezconsult.es
        
        U->>A: Username + Password
        A->>A: Validate Credentials (1FA)
        A->>U: Request TOTP Code
        U->>A: TOTP Code (2FA)
        A->>A: Validate TOTP
        A->>R: Store Session
        A-->>U: Set Session Cookie<br/>Redirect to Original URL
    end
    
    A->>R: Validate Session
    R-->>A: Session Valid
    A-->>C: 200 OK + User Headers
    deactivate A
    
    Note right of C: User Authenticated<br/>Remote-User: rubenalvarezdev
    
    C->>N: Proxy Request<br/>+ Auth Headers
    activate N
    
    N->>R: Get User Session
    R-->>N: Session Data
    N->>D: Query User Data
    D-->>N: User Files & Settings
    N-->>C: Response (Nextcloud UI)
    deactivate N
    
    C-->>U: HTTPS Response<br/>Nextcloud Dashboard
    deactivate C
    
    Note over U,D: ✅ All traffic encrypted<br/>✅ All requests authenticated
